London Ontario's City Budget API

== Development Setup ==

Clone the project to a web-accessible folder.

	git clone git@github.com:rtraction/citybudget.git citybudgetapi

Edit system/application/config/config.php and put your URL into $config['base_url'].

Configure your database settings in system/application/config/database.php.

Run citybudget.sql into your database.

That's it! Most important files are in
	system/application/controllers/
	system/application/models/
	system/application/views/

Cheers!
